<!-- 
    ALL-IN-ONE USER PROFILE
    BY PANDAPPUCCINO
    
    == WHAT IS THIS? ==
    I have come to adore using tabs for keeping content organized.  So nice.
    
    This is an all-in-one profile code that includes a quick-reference for your favorite characters to show off, snippets of your writing, a commission tab for pricing and tracking, a contact tab, and some freebie tabs that you can customize with whatever you want (moodboards, playlists, etc.) or just get rid of if you don't want them.
    
    The tabs are relatively modular.  Don't need the commission tab?  Just get rid of it.  Want to make this a character profile?  Add other tabs (or go check out my Tabbed Character Profile code)!  The world's your oyster!
    
    == HOW DO I USE IT? ==
    Just edit each section as needed!  There are comments to clarify each part for you.
    
    == WHAT'S THE CATCH? ==
    Just keep my credit intact; that's all I ask.
    
    == COMMON EDITING TIPS ==
    1) You can change the particular Bootstrap colors by replacing the color classes (such as bg-dark).  If you would prefer to remove the Bootstrap colors and use your own colors, just remove the entire color class and, in the given "style" section, add "background:" followed by a color, either a hex color or rgb/rgba value.
    2) You can remove the capitalization of the titles by removing the "text-uppercase" class from a given section.
    3) You can use inline color styling by using <span></span> tags in tandem with either Bootstrap color classes or custom color styling.
	
-->

